RAM (7.50 usable)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow does KSP run!? My computer is weak, but the CPU is more powerful than that, yet it can lag really bad, is that a personal laptop, and KSP is on a desktop?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd... I don\u0027t have anything for this thread, I don\u0027t have/know of any flight sims that you could have.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-08T23:50:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222623115\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022141476\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221465429719\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152800\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceception\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Spaceception said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow does KSP run!? My computer is weak, but the CPU is more powerful than that, yet it can lag really bad, is that a personal laptop, and KSP is on a desktop?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd... I don\u0027t have anything for this thread, I don\u0027t have/know of any flight sims that you could have.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt barely runs. But I live with the pain.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell I\u0027ll live if its a few GHz above mine, but I need to know what.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-08T23:55:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00